{"tid":2275273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日(8/11 星期日)係周梓樂逝世一周年","createTime":"2020-11-07T04:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T02:02:18.000Z","uid":33577,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"45be3f71b23b90d2cc4f24b18753ea0de95b364c","tid":2275273,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U61Juxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU61Juxu.jpg&h=554aa83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/%e5%91%a8%e6%a2%93%e6%a8%82%e9%80%9d%e4%b8%96%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4-%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%b9%9f%e6%ad%a3%e5%9c%a8%e6%b6%88%e4%ba%a1/?fbclid=IwAR2g-jmo0tB29AURuDN2jjLRvkIaRDw-EycfGLTwYfl-ER6KZj5BTK0RH2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%25e5%2591%25a8%25e6%25a2%2593%25e6%25a8%2582%25e9%2580%259d%25e4%25b8%2596%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e4%25b9%259f%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b6%2588%25e4%25ba%25a1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2g-jmo0tB29AURuDN2jjLRvkIaRDw-EycfGLTwYfl-ER6KZj5BTK0RH2M&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=e5aba25e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/%e5%91%a8%e6%a2%93%e6%a8%82%e9%80%9d%e4%b8%96%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4-%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%b9%9f%e6%ad%a3%e5%9c%a8%e6%b6%88%e4%ba%a1/?fbclid=IwAR2g-jmo0tB29AURuDN2jjLRvkIaRDw-EycfGLTwYfl-ER6KZj5BTK0RH2M</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">「一些香港人周日可能會到停車場悼念，如果去的話要戴上口罩，限聚令下最多4人一組。確定要和平地致意，不要喊獨立口號，避免放置鮮花。鞠躬後即離開，不要逗留，遵守所有規定，行使我們特首聲稱香港仍然擁有的自由。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得黑警點阻住救護車？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=92GfPoRaqMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D92GfPoRaqMA&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=db564b11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=92GfPoRaqMA</a> <br />\n<br />\n1:17<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c9c5646adbf8c10953e6d33956715f2d4e52ce","tid":2275273,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61c7a4352210c950ba629f10f61f21803d21423","tid":2275273,"uid":33577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"唔一定要去尚十悼念<br />\n但希望大家唔好忘記梓樂<br />\n佢嘅死因依然沉冤未雪<br />\n<br />\n如果去嘅話<br />\n小心埋伏<br />\n只需帶一支鮮花就可以<br />\n明天見"},{"pid":"550d361cb2ae543adaf40a309983f477f81dad6d","tid":2275273,"uid":33577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"有心手足麻煩幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e586d929f484a6b3077a775fbce45f2ffe10be","tid":2275273,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19e06d22e303c849cd6787dffd05366d962f9921","tid":2275273,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"677301a1cdc0272aff3fca8018c042c6cbdbb30a","tid":2275273,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:36:25.000Z","msg":"毋忘梓樂"},{"pid":"c971e99ed9387f14cb4c577949cd87952da25c8c","tid":2275273,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e06d22e303c849cd6787dffd05366d962f9921","tid":2275273,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2cd1ea3c00f59fedd072415d6f637a90b06e30","tid":2275273,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit